# - find RDKit
# RDKIT_INCLUDE_DIR - Where to find RDKit header files (directory)
# RDKIT_FINGERPRINT_LIBRARY - RDKit Fingerprint library
# RDKIT_SMILESPARSE_LIBRARY - RDKit SmilesParse library
# RDKIT_FOUND - Set to TRUE if we found everything (library, includes and executable)

